{"tid":977360,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 喂繼續分享 陳百強 舊歌吖多謝 😊","createTime":"2019-01-11T06:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T10:06:22.000Z","uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9020a64e3ebb137648df80381744de02a4fa9cb","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"送上 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">地下裁判團</span></strong>，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ForE4zHyqVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FForE4zHyqVs&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bb84dadc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ForE4zHyqVs</a><br />\n<br />\n改編自 Pet Shop Boys <strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">It's A Sin</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bTRs93RMarE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbTRs93RMarE&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=fc7ef4cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bTRs93RMarE</a><br />\n<br />\n吖多謝 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cea458084ebf52794eb833bb5ed3a0f219fec112","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"點吖，聽完上面兩首認為邊首好d <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0264c43b8dc47b64290552ffb3a4fedadb4f5e3e","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"陳百強曾經改篇Pet Shop Boys名作&rdquo;It&rsquo;s A Sin&rdquo;成為「地下裁判團」，歌詞內容上雖不盡相同，但同樣是<strong>控訴被無故定罪</strong>。翻查資料，原來此曲的靈感來自Pet Shop Boys成員過去在天主教學校成長的負面經歷：<strong>很多生活樂事都被指摘為犯罪</strong>，故以此曲發洩沮喪和憤怒。這帶出一個根本性的問題：<strong>基督信仰中提及的「罪」是到是甚麼？</strong>"},{"pid":"83cd8fa1f7fba2077ba237a4c3b2084cf97aabe3","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「誰令我總似犯了罪」？</span><br />\n<br />\n說起罪，無法避免回到創世記三1&ndash;12之中那「原罪事件」。這個人類始祖的故事人所共知之餘，其實也有流傳很多不同的詮釋和疑問，就如「分辨善惡樹」是否透過食用來讓人類學習分辨善惡？人類始祖大概是<strong>具有分辨善惡的能力</strong>，因為女人受蛇的引誘之時懂得拒絕。這表示她知道她有<strong>兩個選項</strong>：聽從上主和聽從自己。「分辨善惡樹」的果子就成為這兩個選項之間的<strong>界線</strong>。這果子在女人眼中能夠「使人有智慧」，呼應著蛇所說的「就像上主一樣知道善惡」。假若始祖早已能分辨善惡，人心裡渴望得到的就必然是「像上主一樣」。這正正與新約雅各書一13&ndash;15有所共鳴：「每一個人被誘惑，其實是被自己的私慾所牽纏、所引誘」，始祖以致人類犯罪的責任不在「不誘惑人」的上主，也不在蛇，<strong>乃在乎自己</strong>。"},{"pid":"2659c10994f4a148585fb800ac302c06f539ede4","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vj_7vTsYco8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvj_7vTsYco8&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a51cb63c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vj_7vTsYco8</a><br />\n<br />\n冰！封！的！心！ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0386cfb9a48e4cf526203684acc2b891504a5690","tid":977360,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"神仙也移民<br />\n講1997年前夕 香港人移民"},{"pid":"ca919cec920a9b5a794f11682377b91512f30536","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神仙也移民<br />\n講1997年前夕 香港人移民</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zy6dqQT7N