target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QRpqVRlutkw</a></blockquote><br />\n有舊歌就有薑汁兄  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e624db32afa0dce65c3b4a02c57b31bafd5b8770","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SzAsY064_G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSzAsY064_G0&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bf5480d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SzAsY064_G0</a><br />\n<br />\n陳百強、張國榮跟鍾保羅組成中環三太子，三人之間也一時瑜亮，深受歡迎。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n中環三太子曾一起拍攝了一部叫《失業生》的電影，不知道大家誰看過。該劇中陳百強飾演一位富家公子，張國榮是個打工者，鍾保羅是一個學生。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n陳百強，張國榮這兩位歌壇巨星大家都很熟悉了，筆者也曾專門的寫過文章介紹過他們倆，鍾保羅呢，大家還記得他嗎，今天就來說說他的故事。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n鍾保羅與陳百強，張國榮齊名，「中環三太子」個個都是大明星，可惜，三位都英年早逝，天妒英才，讓人惋惜，而鍾保羅則是最早去世的那位。"},{"pid":"23e480a836d28cafb074e1773618102172ca5cdb","tid":977360,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ke_O8hRhPOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fke_O8hRhPOQ&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cb1fd8a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ke_O8hRhPOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n上面係喝采 都係有佢三個拍，依套先係失業生  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beb3894d0ca0f44987b32c850e68f22ddc0e5399","tid":977360,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"735f